Name: UCSB
Description: a great university located along the California coast

Name: Joshua Tree Nat'l Park
Description: a beautiful, quiet, yet vivid national park with amazing scenery, giant rocks and scorching heat in the Indio Desert in Southern California

Name: Muir Woods National Monument
Description: a gorgeous forest north of San Franciso, just past the golden gate bridge, including many redwood trees and hiking trails.

Name: Carmel Beach
Description: a very tiny, secluded beach, just a bit south of Monterey, CA on PCH 1. absolutely beautiful waves, with beautiful sunset over the nearby mountains.

Name: Montecito Hot Springs
Description: divine hot springs located in montecito hills near Santa Barbara, requires beautiful 1.5 mile hike uphill to reach, but well worth it once there as springs are so relaxing

Name: Alamitos Beach
Description: beautiful beach front in Long Beach City with boardwalk for running, walking, biking, and skating. Gorgeous surroundings with city and businesses all within walking distance.
